科拉亚是捷克海盗党在{{le|2019年欧洲议会选举 (捷克)|2019 European Parliament election in the Czech Republic|2019年欧洲议会选举}}的主要候选人<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.idnes.cz/volby/evropsky-parlament/2019/pirati-volba-lidra-eurovolby-celostatni-forum.A190119_101050_domaci_kop|title = Piráti chtějí vyhrát eurovolby, příští parlamentní volby a sestavit vládu|website = idnes|date = 2019-01-19|language = cs|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2021-01-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210117170837/https://www.idnes.cz/volby/evropsky-parlament/2019/pirati-volba-lidra-eurovolby-celostatni-forum.A190119_101050_domaci_kop|dead-url = no}}</ref>，他与{{le|马克塔·格列哥罗娃|Markéta Gregorová}}和{{le|米库拉什·佩克萨|Mikuláš Peksa}}一起当选为[[欧洲议会议员|欧洲议会议员]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://volby.cz/pls/ep2019/ep2111?xjazyk=CZ&xv=1&xt=2&xstrana=27|title = Volby do Evropského parlamentu konané na území České republiky ve dnech 24.05. – 25.05.2019|website = volby|date = 2019-05-25|language = cs|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2021-04-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411011254/https://volby.cz/pls/ep2019/ep2111?xjazyk=CZ&xv=1&xt=2&xstrana=27|dead-url = no}}</ref>。他的政治议程侧重于[[数字权利|数字权利]]和防止日益严重的[[互联网审查|互联网审查]]；[[环境保护|环境保护]]<ref name="Deník 11.2.2019."/>如逐步[[化石燃料淘汰|淘汰化石燃料]]和尽量减少[[废物|废物]]污染<ref name="ČT24 7. 5. 2019">{{Cite web|url = https://ct24.ceskatelevize.cz/domaci/2807954-rozhovory-s-lidry-kandidatek-do-evropskych-voleb-marcel-kolaja-pirati|title = Rozhovory s lídry kandidátek do evropských voleb: Marcel Kolaja (Piráti)|website = Ceska televize|date = 2019-05-07|language = cs|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2020-11-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201105023627/https://ct24.ceskatelevize.cz/domaci/2807954-rozhovory-s-lidry-kandidatek-do-evropskych-voleb-marcel-kolaja-pirati|dead-url = no}}</ref>；[[消费者保护|消费者保护]]<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.e15.cz/volby/volby-do-evropskeho-parlamentu-2019/piraty-povede-do-eurovoleb-softwarovy-specialista-marcel-kolaja-1355527|title = Piráty povede do eurovoleb softwarový specialista Marcel Kolaja|website = e15|date = 2019-01-19|language = cs|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2021-01-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118052130/https://www.e15.cz/volby/volby-do-evropskeho-parlamentu-2019/piraty-povede-do-eurovoleb-softwarovy-specialista-marcel-kolaja-1355527|dead-url = no}}</ref>，解决欧盟在世界市场上的技术竞争力问题，限制企业在欧盟的[[游说|游说]]活动<ref name="Czech Radio 19 January 2019"/>。他的首要任务之一是解决[[跨国公司|跨国公司]]通过[[避税港|避税港]][[离岸金融中心|离岸利润]]获利的[[避税|避税]]问题<ref name="ČT24 7. 5. 2019"/>。

2019年6月，科拉亚与其他三位[[欧洲海盗党|欧洲海盗党]]议员一起加入了欧洲议会的[[绿党/欧洲自由联盟|绿党/欧洲自由联盟]]党团<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.facebook.com/greensefa/photos/a.394271483967042/2383719451688892/?type=3&theater|title = We are pleased to announce that a further five MEPs have joined the Greens/EFA group! |website=Facebook |author = Greens/EFA in the European Parliament|date = 2019-06-04 |language = en|accessdate = 2020-10-26}}</ref>。7月3日，他被选为欧洲议会14位{{le|欧洲议会副主席|Vice-President of the European Parliament|副主席}}之一<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20190627IPR55411/the-new-european-parliament-vice-presidents|title = The new European Parliament Vice-Presidents|website = News European Parliament|date = 2019-07-03|language = en|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2020-11-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108013436/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20190627IPR55411/the-new-european-parliament-vice-presidents|dead-url = no}}</ref>。科拉亚作为{{le|欧洲议会主席团|Bureau of the European Parliament}}成员，担任[[信息及通信技术|信息及通信技术]]创新战略工作组副主席和{{le|欧洲议会内部市场和消费者保护委员会|European Parliament Committee on the Internal Market and Consumer Protection}}成员<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.europarl.europa.eu/meps/en/197546/MARCEL_KOLAJA/home|title = Marcel KOLAJA|website = MEPs European Parliament|language = en|accessdate = 2020-10-26|archive-date = 2021-03-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210306155133/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/meps/en/197546/MARCEL_KOLAJA/home|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

